Package de.szut.dqi12.cheftrainer.connectorlib.dataexchange

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Community
    The Community Model class, which saves all necessary for a Community.
    Formation
    The Formation class is used to represent the Formation of a Manager.
    FormationFactory
    This class transforms a Position String to a Formation object.
    Manager
    The Manager class stores all information about an Users manager in one Community.
    Market
    This class is the model class for the transfer market.
    MarketPlayer
    This class is used, to present a Player in a JavaFX Table
    Match
    This class is the model class for a match.
    Player
    The player class stores all nested information about a player.
    PlayerLabel
    A Label which contains required informations and methods for a Player.
    Position
    This class just stores the Position, which are possible.
    RealTeam
    The RealTeam class is used to present a RealTeam, not the team of a manager.
    Sendable
    This class should be used for dataexchange objects, which should be send to the Server or Client
    Session
    This class is used to save session specific attributes.
    Transaction
    This class is the model class for each transaction.
    User
    The user class saves all information about the user, who has been logged in at the client.
